ZH: 我家的宅子很大，有五个卧室和一个游泳池。
EN: My house is very big, with five bedrooms and a swimming pool.

ZH: 我们的宅子离市中心很远。
EN: Our house is far away from the city center.

ZH: 这个宅子有个漂亮的花园。
EN: This house has a beautiful garden.

ZH: 这座宅子年代比较久远。
EN: This house is quite old.

ZH: 她在宅子里找到了一张古老的地图。
EN: She found an ancient map in the house.

ZH: 我在宅子里装了一个家庭影院。
EN: I installed a home theater in the house.

ZH: 他们的宅子是一栋现代风格的建筑。
EN: Their house is a modern-style building.

ZH: 我的宅子是用红砖砌成的。
EN: My house is made of red bricks.

ZH: 那个宅子有一个大阳台，可以观赏美景。
EN: That house has a big balcony, where you can enjoy the beautiful view.

ZH: 这座宅子的外墙上爬满了藤蔓植物。
EN: The exterior walls of this house are covered with vines.

ZH: 我们的宅子有一个很大的露天游泳池。
EN: Our house has a large outdoor swimming pool.

ZH: 她每天下班后都会到宅子的花园里散步。
EN: She takes a walk in the garden of her house every day after work.

ZH: 我们的宅子对面有一个公园。
EN: There is a park across from our house.

ZH: 他们在宅子前面种了很多鲜花。
EN: They planted a lot of flowers in front of the house.

ZH: 我们在宅子周围修了一圈围墙。
EN: We built a fence around the house.

ZH: 那个宅子的门口有一个美丽的喷泉。
EN: There is a beautiful fountain at the entrance of that house.

ZH: 这座宅子有一个专门的娱乐室。
EN: This house has a dedicated entertainment room.

ZH: 我们的宅子后面有一个小果园。
EN: There is a small orchard behind our house.

ZH: 我喜欢在宅子里阅读书籍，感觉很安静。
EN: I like reading books in the house, it feels very peaceful.

ZH: 那座宅子被一片茂密的树林所环绕。
EN: That house is surrounded by a dense forest.
